l reproducibility. Supports everything from short-term trading to long-term holding.\",\"cons_desc\":\"While highly functional, response times may decrease during high loads or certain trading costs may apply. Please consider carefully based on your individual investment goals.\"},\"position_checker\":{\"sub_header\":\"Synapse Position Checker v2.0\",\"last_analysis\":\"Last Analysis\",\"hero_badge\":\"Synapse AI Intelligence\",\"hero_title\":\"AI Strategy Verification Terminal\",\"hero_desc\":\"Your investment plan (tickers, prices, risk settings) is multi-dimensionally verified by a group of institutional-level specialist AIs. Three personified AIs with advanced expertise in macro correlations, volatility prediction, and order book imbalances sharply critique and review your strategy from their unique perspectives.\",\"form_title\":\"Input Analysis Scenario\",\"form_desc\":\"Please freely enter the outline of the trade you want to verify (entry rationale, expected time horizon, risk tolerance, etc.).\",\"asset_class\":\"Asset Class Selection\",\"fx\":\"Forex (FX)\",\"stocks\":\"Stocks (STOCKS)\",\"crypto\":\"Crypto (CRYPTO)\",\"ticker_selection\":\"Ticker Selection\",\"direction\":\"Direction\",\"buy\":\"Buy\",\"sell\":\"Sell\",\"entry_target\":\"Entry Target\",\"stop_loss_limit\":\"Stop Loss Limit\",\"take_profit_target\":\"Take Profit Target\",\"validate_plan\":\"Verify Plan Validity\",\"loading_1\":\"🌐 Synchronizing macro correlation data...\",\"loading_2\":\"📊 Running order book imbalance protocol...\",\"loading_3\":\"⚖️ Simulating risk governance...\",\"loading_4\":\"💎 Generating premium strategy scenarios...\",\"report_summary\":\"Strategy Verification Report: Summary\",\"plan_label\":\"{ticker} {direction} Plan\",\"overall_eval\":\"Executive Summary: Overall Evaluation\",\"expert_01_title\":\"01 Chief Macro Strategist\",\"expert_01_role\":\"Expertise\",\"expert_01_desc\":\"Major central bank policies, interest rate trends, and global asset correlation deep 