isk-Off.\",\"sync_rate\":\"Synapse Sync Rate\",\"consistency_alert\":\"Inconsistency Alert: {level}\",\"view_details\":\"Deep Analysis →\",\"modal_terminal_details\":\"Synapse Terminal Details\",\"current_status\":\"Current Status\",\"sync_consistency\":\"Sync Consistency\",\"mtf_analysis\":\"Multi-Timeframe Analysis\",\"bullish_edge\":\"Bullish Edge\",\"bearish_edge\":\"Bearish Edge\",\"neutral_edge\":\"Neutral\",\"ai_diagnosis\":\"Synapse AI Diagnosis\",\"diagnosis_high\":\"Fewer inconsistencies, expecting price action following technical indicators.\",\"diagnosis_low\":\"Noise detected in some indicators, caution for sudden volatility. AI detects attempts to break resistance.\",\"status_stable\":\"Stable\",\"status_syncing\":\"Syncing\",\"status_in_progress\":\"In Progress\",\"status_divergent\":\"Divergent\",\"cons_high\":\"High\",\"cons_mid\":\"Mid\",\"cons_low\":\"Low\",\"diagnosis_text\":\"The Synapse AI engine has analyzed {pair} with a synchronization rate of {sync}%. The current diagnosis indicates: {detail}\",\"usd_theme_desc_title\":\"US Rate Expectations\",\"jpy_theme_desc_title\":\"BoJ Policy Pivot\"},\"crypto_pro\":{\"hero_badge\":\"Crypto Intelligence v2.4 Live\",\"hero_title\":\"AI thoroughly analyzes the crypto market.\",\"hero_desc\":\"From BTC to SOL, covering everything from major tickers to emerging L1s. AI monitors whale movements and DEX volume to capture the waves of volatility.\",\"terminal_title\":\"Crypto Synapse Terminal\",\"onchain_synced\":\"On-chain Synced\",\"advanced_analysis_layer\":\"Advanced Analysis Layer\",\"market_inter_sync\":\"Inter-market Sync Analysis\",\"btc_vs_us10y_title\":\"BTC vs US 10Y\",\"btc_vs_us10y_desc\":\"BTC's hedge function in a rising rate environment is declining. Correlation as a risk asset is becoming clearer.\",\"onchain_pulse\":\"On-chain Pulse\",\"whale_accumulation_title\":\"Whale Accumulation Status\",\"whale_accumulation_desc\":\"Inflow to major exchanges is decreasing. Whales' transfer to cold wall